{"id":583413,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/04/【立此存照】这是两个北大之间的斗争/","date":"2018-04-23T16:42:18Z","modified":"2018-04-23T16:42:18Z","title":"【立此存照】这是“两个北大”之间的斗争","content":"<p>图片来自网络，出现在北大校园，据悉目前已被撕去&#8230;&#8230;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">声援勇士岳昕</p>\n<p>昨天，意味多年力行公益的北大同学终于因为关心一件最切身的公共事务，依法申请信息公开，而被深夜约谈，以致母亲精神崩溃，自己失去自由，我们这些匿名者，敬佩岳同学具名上书的勇气，更钦慕他临事不惧的正气，而有司诸公你们究竟在怕什么？岳同学最怕的是，对不起百廿年前的五四先辈，毁了精神上的校庆，而你们最怕的是“出乱子”毁了政绩上的校庆，我们于是想问，这到底是谁和谁的斗争？这是“两个北大”之间的斗争。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right\">湖底群魂</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/image_uploaded_from_ios.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-583414\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/image_uploaded_from_ios.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/image_uploaded_from_ios.jpg 1440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/image_uploaded_from_ios-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/image_uploaded_from_ios-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/image_uploaded_from_ios-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[33760,20821,15854,10227,34431,34297,8714,34425,34306,20813,34020,25952,9503,9212,34298,34267,34432,34269]}